'''Improvement Support Systems (ISS)''' are [[computer]]ized or electronic specialized systems that help to improve processes, resources, [[Product (business)|product]]s, [[business]]es, and so on.
Examples of ISS are systems that help to improve: *[[Industrial production]] *Financial indicators ([[Balanced scorecard|Balance Scorecard]]) *Industrial quality, by using for example [[Statistical process control|Statistical Process Control]] (SPC) techniques.
